<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/28315774">三国中蒯家的结局如何？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3508947" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">对荆州几度转手后荆州几大家族的情况很感兴趣，但三国志中貌似没提及，请历史大神解惑</div>


</div>
